Ubong Williams bụ onye na-agba bọọlụ na-agba dị ka onye na-agbachite bara uru na onye etiti fiilidu nke Abia Warriors
Ọ dị mbụ gbaara ndi Delta Force

Ubong Williams Edet malitere egwuregwu bọọlụ ya site n'otu ndị ntorobịa ya bụ Karamone FC bụ ndị mechara gbazinye ya nye ndị Delta Force FC ndi Otu Mbà Naijiria  tupu ọ banye Abia Warriors site na otu nne na nna ya bukwa Karamone FC.
